14 SECTION 2. EXTRA HELP - OIL AND GAS COMMISSION. There is hereby
15 authorized, for the Department of Energy and Environment - Oil and Gas
16 Commission for the 2025-2026 fiscal year, the following maximum number of
17 part-time or temporary employees, to be known as "Extra Help", payable from
18 funds appropriated herein for such purposes: six (6) temporary or part-time
19 employees, when needed, at rates of pay not to exceed those provided in the
20 Uniform Classification and Compensation Act, or its successor, or this act
21 for the appropriate classification.
